p To disable a button, use attributes <code>disabled</code> and <code>tabindex="-1"</code>. The latter is to ensure that the button cannot be focused with the keyboard (for accessibility purposes).
p: a.button href="#default-buttons" disabled=true tabindex="-1" Call to action
p: a.button-small href="#default-buttons" disabled=true tabindex="-1" Call to action
p: a.button-small.with-arrow href="#default-buttons" disabled=true tabindex="-1" Call to action
